ky items?"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t",["LI",{"class":"contents__listitem"},"\n",["A",{"class":"contents__list-link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/clinical-or-hazardous-waste"},"What should I do with clinical or hazardous waste?"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t",["LI",{"class":"contents__listitem"},"\n",["A",{"class":"contents__list-link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/clinical-sharps"},"What should I do with clinical sharps?"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t",["LI",{"class":"contents__listitem"},"\n",["A",{"class":"contents__list-link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/article/9092/What-should-I-do-if-I-discover-fly-tipped-waste"},"What should I do if I discover fly-tipped waste?"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t",["LI",{"class":"contents__listitem"},"\n",["A",{"class":"contents__list-link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/bin-storage-and-collection-guidance-to-developers"},"Bin storage and collection - guidance to developers"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t"],"\n"],["DIV",{"class":"a-title","id":"_content_"},"\n\t",["H2",{},"About waste management"],"\n"],"\n\n\n\n\t",["DIV",{"class":"a-body a-body--documentsection"},"\n\n\n",["P",{},"The Council is committed to reducing the amount of waste that is generated locally. As a local authority we are responsible for collecting bins and waste in the Borough."],["P",{},"We provide three waste collections:"],["UL",{},["LI",{},"black bins for household rubbish "],["LI",{},"green bins for recycling "],["LI",{},"brown bins for garden waste (subscription service)"]],["P",{"class":"alert alert--info"},"The Council has implemented a ",["A",{"class":"a-body__link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/policies/waste-collection"},"Waste collection policy"]," which details how the various collection services operates and any rules relating to utilising these services"],["P",{},"We are also a member of Norfolk Recycles, a scheme run by Norfolk County Council and local authorities in the area aimed at:"],["UL",{},["LI",{},"providing a quality recycling service across the whole of Norfolk"],["LI",{},"reducing the amount of rubbish collected in the residual waste bins"]],["P",{},"You can find out more about the scheme, including ways you can recycle more at home and at work, on the ",["A",{"class":"a-body__link a-body__link--external","href":"https://www.norfolkrecycles.com/","target":"_blank"},"Norfolk Recycles",["SPAN",{"class":"media-link__newwindow"}," (opens new window)"]]," website."],"\n\t"],"\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t",["DIV",{"class":"document-pagination"},"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t",["A",{"href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/article/2340/Where-is-the-tip-recycling-centre","class":"document-pagination__link document-pagination__link--next"},"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",["SPAN",{"class":"document-pagination__direction"},"Next"],"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",["SPAN",{"class":"accessibility"},":"],"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",["SPAN",{"class":"document-pagination__pagetitle"},"Where is the tip/recycling centre?"],"\n\t\t\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t",["DIV",{"class":"document-print"},"\n\t\t\t",["A",{"href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/rubbish-and-recycling?action=Print&model=%232331+-+%27Rubbish+and+recycling%27%3a+document","target":"_blank"},["SPAN",{"class":"document-print__text"},"Print entire document"],["SPAN",{"class":"document-print__newwindow accessibility"}," (opens in new browser window or tab)"]],"\n\t\t"],"\n\n\n","\n\n\n\t","\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t\t",["DIV",{"class":"a-pagemodifieddate"},"\n\t",["SPAN",{"class":"a-pagemodifieddate__date"},"Last modified on 27 March 2025"],"\n"],["DIV",{"class":"a-share"},"\n\t\t",["P",{"class":"a-share__label"},"Share this page"],"\n\t\t",["A",{"class":"a-share__link","target":"_blank","href":"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/article/8296/About-waste-management"},["SPAN",{"class":"blanktarget__text"},["IMG",{"__playwright_current_src__":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/images/social/facebook.p