"My bin has been damaged or lost, what can I do?"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t",["LI",{"class":"contents__listitem"},"\n",["A",{"class":"contents__list-link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/article/3371/What-happens-if-I-move-home"},"What happens if I move home?"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t",["LI",{"class":"contents__listitem"},"\n",["A",{"class":"contents__list-link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/article/2931/I-have-just-moved-to-a-new-build-property-how-do-I-order-refuse-bins"},"I have just moved to a new build property - how do I order refuse bins?"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t",["LI",{"class":"contents__listitem"},"\n",["A",{"class":"contents__list-link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/article/2338/Can-I-donate-unwanted-items"},"Can I donate unwanted items?"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t",["LI",{"class":"contents__listitem"},"\n",["A",{"class":"contents__list-link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/article/2339/What-should-I-do-with-trade-waste"},"What should I do with trade waste?"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t",["LI",{"class":"contents__listitem"},"\n",["A",{"class":"contents__list-link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/bulky-items"},"Will you collect household bulky items?"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t",["LI",{"class":"contents__listitem"},"\n",["A",{"class":"contents__list-link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/clinical-or-hazardous-waste"},"What should I do with clinical or hazardous waste?"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t",["LI",{"class":"contents__listitem"},"\n",["A",{"class":"contents__list-link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/clinical-sharps"},"What should I do with clinical sharps?"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t",["LI",{"class":"contents__listitem"},"\n",["A",{"class":"contents__list-link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/article/9092/What-should-I-do-if-I-discover-fly-tipped-waste"},"What should I do if I discover fly-tipped waste?"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t\t\t",["LI",{"class":"contents__listitem"},"\n",["A",{"class":"contents__list-link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/bin-storage-and-collection-guidance-to-developers"},"Bin storage and collection - guidance to developers"],"\t\t\t"],"\n\t"],"\n"],["DIV",{"class":"a-title"},"\n\t",["H2",{},"How do I find my bin collection day?"],"\n"],"\n\n\n\n\t",["DIV",{"class":"a-body a-body--documentsection"},"\n\n\n",["P",{},"We empty green recycle bins and black waste bins on alternate weeks. Check your bin collection dates by entering your postcode on our ",["A",{"class":"a-body__link","href":"https://myaccount.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/find-my-waste-collection-days"},"Find my waste collection days"]," page."],["P",{"class":"alert alert--info"},"Make sure that the correct bin is left at the edge of your property, on the kerb or at your collection point with the handles facing the road, ready for collection by 6.30am. You may leave your bin out ready for collection no earlier than 6pm the evening before collection, the bin must then be returned to within your property boundary as soon as possible after emptying and must be stored within your property boundaries between collections."],["P",{},"Communal bins work in the same way as household ones."],["P",{},"You can ",["A",{"class":"a-body__link","href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/article/2687/Request-an-assisted-bin-collection"},"request an assisted bin collection"]," if there is no one in the property who is able to move your bin. You can apply for an extra black/green bin if there are more than five people in your house, or five including a nappy need. Call ",["A",{"class":"a-body__link","href":"https://www.greatyarmouthservices.co.uk/contact-us"},"Great Yarmouth Services Ltd"]," for advice."],["P",{},"If your property is on a sack collection scheme, please do not put your sacks out before 6.30am on your collection day."],"\n\t"],"\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\t\t\t",["DIV",{"class":"document-pagination"},"\n\t\t\t\t\t",["A",{"href":"https://www.great-yarmouth.gov.uk/article/2340/Where-is-the-tip-recycling-ce